## Key Foreign Key Relationships

### users (Central Entity)
```sql
users.id → students.userId
users.id → teachers.userId
users.id → parents.userId
users.id → counselors.userId
users.id → user_roles.userId
users.id → studentApplications.studentId
users.schoolId → schools.id
users.parentId → users.id (self-reference for parent-child)
```

### schools (Tenant Root)
```sql
schools.id → users.schoolId
schools.id → students.schoolId
schools.id → teachers.schoolId
schools.id → classes.schoolId
schools.id → subscriptions.schoolId
schools.id → invoices.schoolId
schools.districtId → districts.id
```

### assessments (Career Matching)
```sql
assessments.id → assessmentResults.assessmentId
assessments.userId → users.id
assessments.id → careerMatches.assessmentId
careers.id → careerMatches.careerId
```

### Library
```sql
books.id → circulation.bookId
libraryMembers.id → circulation.memberId
books.schoolId → schools.id
```

### RBAC
```sql
roles.id → user_roles.roleId
users.id → user_roles.userId
permissions.id → role_permissions.permissionId
roles.id → role_permissions.roleId
```

