## Table Index Strategy

### High-Query Columns (Indexed)
- `users.clerkUserId` - Authentication lookups
- `users.schoolId` - Tenant filtering
- `users.type` - Portal routing
- `users.isActive` - Active user filtering
- `schools.code` - School code lookup
- `schools.subscriptionStatus` - Billing queries
- `assessments.userId` - Student assessments
- `careerMatches.studentId` - Career recommendations
- `invoices.schoolId` - Invoice queries
- `circulation.bookId` - Book tracking
- `circulation.memberId` - Member tracking

